@GovInslee # of cases is irrelevant. # of deaths relative to society is what matters. The state, national, and global death rate for COVID-19 does not justify ANY of your dictates, demands,  or policies.

And cloth/fabric masks have near ZERO efficacy against the spread of the virus; ZERO.
